Single\-line output format.
.TP
\f[B]\(enjson\f[R]
Output results as JSON to stderr.
.TP
\f[B]\(enstdout\f[R]
Write the summary to stdout instead of stderr.
.TP
\f[B]\(encolor\f[R]
Force coloured output (overrides \f[B]NO_COLOR\f[R]).
.TP
\f[B]\(enno\-color\f[R]
Disable coloured output.
.TP
\f[B]\(endescribe\f[R]
Emit structured JSON metadata for AI agents.
.TP
\f[B]\(enversion\f[R]
Show version.
.TP
\f[B]\-h\f[R], \f[B]\(enhelp\f[R]
Show help.
.SH OUTPUT FORMATS
\f[B]Default\f[R] (multi\-line, stderr):
.IP
